description:
My place is close to JFK Airport, Subway Station, Grocery Store, Shopping Centers, St.John University. Outside balcony. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.

You have access to the entire house. The room upstairs is not visible. So you will have privacy.

Public transportation is a block away.

Yes
name: Artsy One bedroom Apartment
review: Beautiful home love the privacy !! The host was extremely nice I would love to stay again on my next trip!! Wonderful place overall ❤️
